    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受经典冒险与解谜游戏启发，在《滑滑史莱姆》中，你将化身为一只粉嫩Q弹的可爱史莱姆，依着本能一路往前滑，探索充满复古魅力的2D像素世界，解决一个个惊喜的推箱谜题。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>简单操作 + 奇妙反弹 = 纯粹乐趣！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操控史上最可爱的滑行小家伙，<strong>只需上下左右轻点方向。史莱姆会一路滑行，直到“Duang”地撞到障碍物反弹。</strong>你的任务就是利用地图中的墙壁、地形，巧布滑行路线，<strong>引导史莱姆精准“溜”到出口。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151990/extras/cf84eab3744bc021d5e049ad174ac5c8.poster.avif?t=1764832998\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151990/extras/cf84eab3744bc021d5e049ad174ac5c8.webm?t=1764832998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151990/extras/cf84eab3744bc021d5e049ad174ac5c8.mp4?t=1764832998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>跳出盒子！哦对了，横冲直撞也可以</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一场对空间想象力与规划能力的趣味考验。<strong>没有复杂剧情，不设时间与生命限制，只专注于纯粹的解谜乐趣。</strong>每一关都鼓励你跳出固有思维，去发现那些让你忍不住“嗯？原来如此！”的巧妙路径。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151990/extras/d99cfa9018579a894f0c920de0566cc0.poster.avif?t=1764832998\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151990/extras/d99cfa9018579a894f0c920de0566cc0.webm?t=1764832998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151990/extras/d99cfa9018579a894f0c920de0566cc0.mp4?t=1764832998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>可爱像素，手感满分</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >活泼明亮的经典像素风格，搭配真实<strong>丰富的音效与Q弹手感</strong>，完美还原了小史莱姆在不同地图关卡的每一次滑行与反弹。每一次成功解谜，都伴随着这份沉浸的视听体验，让你收获豁然开朗的成就感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151990/extras/8a0fe1af48784c92aa3c332885ed64db.poster.avif?t=1764832998\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151990/extras/8a0fe1af48784c92aa3c332885ed64db.webm?t=1764832998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151990/extras/8a0fe1af48784c92aa3c332885ed64db.mp4?t=1764832998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>宝宝行，奶奶也行</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你想利用碎片时间来一局轻松闯关，还是投入数小时挑战全关卡极限，都能在此找到乐趣。凭借直观的机制与无需语言的共通玩法，所有玩家都能轻松上手——<strong>甚至连奶奶也能跟着史莱姆开心滑行！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151990/extras/056043a678f129277662d9fc43f4f9b9.poster.avif?t=1764832998\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151990/extras/056043a678f129277662d9fc43f4f9b9.webm?t=1764832998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151990/extras/056043a678f129277662d9fc43f4f9b9.mp4?t=1764832998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无需语言支持，全世界的玩家都能轻松上手！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ 关卡, 每个关卡都经过精心设计，等你来挑战！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >史上最可爱的滑行小家伙！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一帧画面都充满细腻与温馨！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越秋日森林、晶莹矿洞、巫师高塔等奇幻场景！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >休闲畅玩或追求极限，全由你决定！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >适合碎片时间小玩一会儿，也适合整天沉浸其中！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次滑行与碰撞都带来极致享受！</p></li></ul>",
